      "zh": "卷七 補帝紀第七 武成帝",
      "en": "Volume 7 Annals 7: Emperor Wucheng",
      "raw": "卷七 補帝紀第七 武成帝 Volume 7 Annals 7: Emperor Wucheng"
    },
    "sentenceCount": 91,
    "translatedCount": 0,
